snippet: The authorities on Monday found the body of a fourth victim deep in the rubble of a parking garage that partially collapsed last week at Miami Dade College.
abstract: Authorities find body of fourth victim in rubble of parking garage that partially collapsed at Miami Dade College in Florida.
lead_paragraph: The authorities on Monday found the body of a fourth victim deep in the rubble of a parking garage that partially collapsed last week at Miami Dade College.

headline.main: Florida: Fourth Victim Found in Collapse of College Garage
